【Sky Parkour】空中跑酷【小游戏】Here comes the exciFHC翻译ting Parkour map! Over 50 different Parkour Level, wait for you to challenge. What are you waiting for? Feel like download and friends conquer the Parkour world together!激动人心的跑酷地图，来了！超过50个不同的跑酷关卡，期待你的挑战。你还在等什么呢？下载地图并和朋友一起征服这个跑酷地图吧！作者：BOLTLV，推特介绍1. The map was made by five people with six hours’unremitting efforts.地图由5个人6个小时不懈地努力制作的。2. There are 60 different Parkour levels and some easy mini games on the map.地图包含60个不同的跑酷关卡和一些简单的小游戏。3. Every level is challenging. Why not take a time to see how long it takes to complete the Parkour map, and then tell me on Twitter?每一关都是具有挑战性的，可以记录下完成的时间然后再推特上告诉我。4. This map supports one or two people to play together. Call your buddies to conquer the Parkour World.地图支持1或2个人一起玩，快叫上的你朋友来征服这个跑酷地图吧！
游戏版本1.11/1.12/1.13下载链接: https://pan.baidu.com/s/1_RuWOXwxHX9NkJe7shaExg
